{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]If you ever get lonesome
[G]And you're down in San Antone
[F]Just beg, steal or [G]borrow
Two nickels or a [E]dime
[Am]Call me on the [F]pho-[C]oo-[G]one
I'll meet you at the Alamo [C]Mission
[G]And we will say our prayers
[F]The Holy Ghost and the [G]Virgin Mother will heal us
[E]As we kneel the[Am]re
{end_of_verse}


{start_of_chorus: Chorus}
In the [F]midnight,[C]
[F]Moonlight,[C]
[G]Midnight, [E]moonlight, mid[C]night
{end_of_chorus}


{start_of_chorus: Chorus}
In the [F]midnight,[C]
[F]Moonlight,[C]
